abstract: The Internet equipment maker benefited from growing demand for bigger, faster networks that can handle video.
snippet: The Internet equipment maker benefited from growing demand for bigger, faster networks that can handle video.
lead_paragraph: The Internet equipment maker Cisco Systems reported a 36 percent jump in profit in its second fiscal quarter yesterday, benefiting from growing demand for bigger, faster networks that can handle video.

headline.main: Video Gear Helps to Lift Cisco’s Profit and Shares
headline.print_headline: Video Gear Helps to Lift Cisco’s Profit And Shares
